@node Main "AlphaQuad - Documentation"

                              AlphaQuad 1.06

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'AlphaQuad' is a @{" game " link play} where you try to place a number of letters in
the right order on a 4 by 4 tiles game board (or a 5 by 5 tiles board,
depending on the game board you play with). When a letter is in the
right position on the board, it will appear in white.

  You can choose between 2 game board sizes, a 4 by 4 tiles board (with
the letters from A to P) or a 5 by 5 tiles board (with the letters from
A to Y).

  Have fun!

